wasn't fast enough.

4
00:00:17.392 --> 00:00:18.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What are you saying?

5
00:00:18.769 --> 00:00:22.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
