barely last four lousy minutes.

7
00:00:28.278 --> 00:00:29.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

8
00:00:29.238 --> 00:00:30.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
See, it's been
getting weaker.

9
00:00:30.614 --> 00:00:32.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't you think I
should've known?

10
00:00:32.658 --> 00:00:34.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why did you keep it
a secret from me?

11
00:00:34.910 --> 00:00:37.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Listen, I... I don't
think I'm gonna make it.

12
00:00:37.663 --> 00:00:39.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Stop talking,
just lay still.

13
00:00:39.456 --> 00:00:40.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But, Bunny...

14
00:00:40.916 --> 00:00:42.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I said, stop it!

15
00:00:42.459 --> 00:00:46.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Chasing after the bad guys with you
and listening to your lame lectures...

16
00:00:47.005 --> 00:00:48.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I loved every
minute of it.

17
00:00:48.674 --> 00:00:51.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The truth is, when you finally
started calling me "Kotetsu,"

18
00:00:51.843 --> 00:00:55.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you made me so happy I went out
on an all-night bender to celebrate.

19
00:00:55.639 --> 00:00:58.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This isn't the end!
Stop talking like that!

20
00:00:58.183 --> 00:01:00.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thanks for everything, buddy.

21
00:01:00.394 --> 00:01:03.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Shut up, Kotetsu!
You're not dying, you hear me?

22
00:01:04.773 --> 00:01:08.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasp] Kotetsu?

23
00:01:08.193 --> 00:01:09.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu!

24
00:01:19.496 --> 00:01:20.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu...

25
00:02:52.506 --> 00:02:55.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
Why is his signal gone?
Why?!

26
00:02:56.093 --> 00:02:59.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>If Tiger's signal's gone,</i>
<i>it means he's gone.</i>

27
00:03:05.185 --> 00:03:06.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Blue Rose]
What happened?

28
00:03:06.645 --> 00:03:09.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He was in trouble.
His powers had been declining lately.

29
00:03:09.981 --> 00:03:11.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

30
00:03:11.274 --> 00:03:13.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When it came down to it,
he told me to fire...

31
00:03:13.944 --> 00:03:15.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
knowing he
wouldn't make it.

32
00:03:16.405 --> 00:03:17.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What are you
saying?!

33
00:03:18.156 --> 00:03:19.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Daddy!

34
00:03:19.825 --> 00:03:20.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu...

35
00:03:20.992 --> 00:03:25.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Wake up, Dad! Please,
you have to wake up! Please, Daddy!

36
00:03:25.789 --> 00:03:27.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sobbing]

37
00:03:29.209 --> 00:03:30.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Maverick] Well done, Barnaby!

38
00:03:31.378 --> 00:03:34.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You managed to defeat H-01.

39
00:03:34.339 --> 00:03:36.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I am very proud to
see this, my boy.

40
00:03:36.883 --> 00:03:39.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You think you'll
get away with this?

41
00:03:39.177 --> 00:03:42.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You took away my parents,
then Samantha,

42
00:03:42.472 --> 00:03:43.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and now, Kotetsu!

43
00:03:43.682 --> 00:03:45.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We're gonna put a
stop to you right now!

44
00:03:45.684 --> 00:03:47.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don't be so sure of that.

45
00:03:47.394 --> 00:03:49.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You planning to mess with
our memories again?!

46
00:03:49.688 --> 00:03:51.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Rock Bison]
Don't even think about it, you Jackass!

47
00:03:52.149 --> 00:03:53.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I won't need to go through
all that trouble.

48
00:03:53.942 --> 00:03:55.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[snaps fingers]

49
00:04:02.200 --> 00:04:04.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Rotwang]
Androids can be marvelous weapons!

50
00:04:05.537 --> 00:04:08.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And unlike you heroes,
they can be mass-produced.

51
00:04:08.707 --> 00:04:11.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't presume victory because
you were able to defeat one of them!

52
00:04:12.419 --> 00:04:13.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, no!

53
00:04:13.503 --> 00:04:15.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why, you!

54
00:04:15.422 --> 00:04:16.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don't do it!

55
00:04:22.179 --> 00:04:23.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

56
00:04:24.681 --> 00:04:25.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Fire Emblem!

57
00:04:39.237 --> 00:04:40.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Look out!

58
00:04:52.292 --> 00:04:53.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

59
00:05:15.714 --> 00:05:16.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

60
00:05:37.587 --> 00:05:40.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You might as well give up.
You won't be able to win!

61
00:05:41.883 --> 00:05:42.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Maverick!

62
00:05:42.968 --> 00:05:45.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, the credit for this
belongs to your parents.

63
00:05:46.012 --> 00:05:48.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>The lethal power demonstrated</i>
<i>by these androids</i>

64
00:05:48.515 --> 00:05:51.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>is based entirely on their research.</i>

65
00:05:51.268 --> 00:05:54.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The truth is, they're the ones
responsible for all of this.

66
00:05:54.604 --> 00:05:55.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're wrong!

67
00:05:55.814 --> 00:05:58.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The research my parents did was
always meant to save people,

68
00:05:58.817 --> 00:06:00.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Not to create
killing machines!

69
00:06:00.569 --> 00:06:01.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[gun blasts]
-Auggh!

70
00:06:07.492 --> 00:06:09.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There's just one
thing left to say.

71
00:06:09.452 --> 00:06:10.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Farewell, heroes.

72
00:06:10.912 --> 00:06:12.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's been a pleasure
knowing you!

73
00:06:12.497 --> 00:06:14.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Time to finish
off these freaks!

74
00:06:14.749 --> 00:06:16.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Damn it all!

75
00:06:24.050 --> 00:06:25.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu...

76
00:06:26.036 --> 00:06:27.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kill them!

77
00:06:39.858 --> 00:06:42.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[powering down]

78
00:06:44.905 --> 00:06:45.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

79
00:06:49.367 --> 00:06:50.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They all stopped!

80
00:06:50.827 --> 00:06:52.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But why?

81
00:06:53.580 --> 00:06:54.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[pings]

82
00:06:54.706 --> 00:06:55.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah!

83
00:06:57.417 --> 00:06:58.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?!

84
00:06:58.752 --> 00:07:00.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They've gone into
safety mode.

85
00:07:01.473 --> 00:07:02.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Wait!

86
00:07:02.464 --> 00:07:03.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, what are you
going to do, sir?

87
00:07:05.842 --> 00:07:08.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm going to reboot the
main system controls.

88
00:07:08.929 --> 00:07:10.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh no, you're not!

89
00:07:18.396 --> 00:07:20.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't let me fall!
Help me, please!

90
00:07:21.024 --> 00:07:22.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let go of me.

91
00:07:22.317 --> 00:07:24.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But Mr. Maverick!
That's suicide!

92
00:07:24.903 --> 00:07:28.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Now that your androids have been
completed, I have no further use for you.

93
00:07:28.823 --> 00:07:32.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But I thought the plan was for us to
exterminate those creepy NEXT together!

94
00:07:33.912 --> 00:07:35.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The trouble is, I'm also a NEXT.

95
00:07:36.081 --> 00:07:37.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

96
00:07:37.999 --> 00:07:40.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

97
00:07:44.005 --> 00:07:45.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That guy's a monster.

98
00:08:00.855 --> 00:08:02.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Dragon Kid]
You're not getting away.

99
00:08:02.440 --> 00:08:03.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Sky High]
Accept your defeat and surrender!

100
00:08:03.984 --> 00:08:05.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Maverick]
You're wasting your time.

101
00:08:05.694 --> 00:08:08.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Even if you were to arrest me,
it wouldn't do you any good.

102
00:08:08.822 --> 00:08:10.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And why is that?

103
00:08:10.323 --> 00:08:14.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Because I have the full respect and trust
of powerful figures in this city.

104
00:08:14.285 --> 00:08:16.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
