all the accusations you want,

105
00:08:17.038 --> 00:08:19.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
but no-one will dare to question me.

106
00:08:19.207 --> 00:08:21.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
